parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Oil Consumption and Engine Failure

symptoms: engine stalling or loss of power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the knock detection system can cause the engine to stall or seize, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: engine stalling or loss of power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the engine control system can cause the engine to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: engine stalling or loss of power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the clutch or transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
vehicle unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the HVAC system can cause a lack of visibility, accidents, and safety risks due to hot air or black smoke coming out of the vents, making it difficult to drive.

black smoke coming out of A/C vents
and inability to see while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the parking brake can cause the vehicle to roll, leading to accidents, injuries, and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: and the driver may be injured or nearly run over.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The spontaneous shattering of the rear windshield can cause accidents, injuries, and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: without any prior damage or warning signs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the vehicle and transmission issues can cause accidents, injuries, and safety risks due to loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when trying to pick up speed

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause accidents, injuries, and safety risks due to loss of control.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels stuck to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The shuttering and stalling of the engine can cause accidents, injuries, and safety risks due to loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause accidents, injuries, and safety risks due to lack of visibility.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to severe injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not protected from the impact.

no warning of failure before the crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light on the dashboard is illuminated
no deployment of airbags in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the fan control switch can cause overheating, electrical fires, and AC failure.
symptoms: and electrical burning smells due to fan control switch failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Battery drain and failure can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Lack of security system can lead to theft and unauthorized access to the vehicle.
